## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="df2aa-102"><xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink>控制項可讓您以程式設計方式存取 HTML`link`伺服器上的項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df2aa-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink> control allows programmatic access to the HTML `link` element on the server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="df2aa-103"><xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink>控制項可用來以程式設計方式在網頁上指定的階層式樣式表 (CSS) 參考。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df2aa-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink> control can be used to programmatically specify a cascading style sheet (CSS) reference in a Web page.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="df2aa-104">下列程式碼範例示範如何使用<xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink>以程式設計方式加入到網頁上的 樣式表的控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df2aa-104">The following code example demonstrates using the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink> control to programmatically add a style sheet to a Web page.</span></span>  
  
 [!code-aspx-csharp[System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink#1](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_WebNet/System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink/CS/htmllinkcs.aspx#1)]
 [!code-aspx-vb[System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink#1](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_WebNet/System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlLink/VB/htmllinkvb.aspx#1)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="df2aa-105">若要執行上述的程式碼範例，您需要的是階層式樣式表 (CSS) 名為`Stylesheet.css`，其中包含下列程式碼，儲存在您的網站與相同的目錄。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="df2aa-105">To run the preceding code example, you need a cascading style sheet (CSS) named `Stylesheet.css`, containing the following code, saved in the same directory as your Web site.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
body {  
  padding-left: 11em;  
  font-family:  Verdana, "Times New Roman",  
        Times, serif;  
  color: blue;  
  background-color: silver }  
h1 {  
  font-family: Helvetica, Geneva, Arial,  
        SunSans-Regular, sans-serif;   
  color: purple }  
```  
  
```csharp  
body {  
